# Kite Staging Environment

The current configuration targets the **staging** environment. When directing the user to visit any kite.ai page, always use `staging.kite.ai` instead of `kite.ai`.

- ❌ `https://kite.ai/...`
- ✅ `https://staging.kite.ai/...`
